column5: AFH My Friday afternoon 2 cents Nothing has changed since alot of us bought in on oversold conditions after the bad news weve had drops on low volume and no negative news since My instinct right now is telling me to be patient and wait Up and down on low volume mean little It is the same with my other position in CNET Also has been downtrending on low volume and has been getting hit by bad trade news No bad news since I bought over a month ago again my instincts are telling me to be patient These kinds of losses on both are fluff and any good news for both will imo send them to recover and more Thanks and happy Friday everyone
